临时防护/缓解策略:
使用AppArmor配置文件限制抽象套接字访问：
profile docker-default flags=(attach_disconnected,mediate_deleted) {
  deny unix addr=@**,
}

使用Ingress或负载均衡器验证Connection头：
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: capsule-proxy-ingress
  annotations:
    nginx.ingress.kubernetes.io/configuration-snippet: |
      if ($http_connection ~* "malicious") {
        return 403;
      }
